         <abstract id="aspace_d0e5a65d476bfbbd55a1e861245e8589">These letters to George Alder Blumer are mainly about the American Medico-Psychological Association and the <emph render="italic">American Journal of Insanity</emph>, edited by Blumer. Several of the writers were, like Blumer, administrators of psychiatric hospitals in the United States and abroad.</abstract>
