            <scopecontent id="aspace_9011709033f006408545f0b6f3761472">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>These letters were sent by George Alder Blumer to Harvey Cushing in 1920 and returned.  They then were sent by Dr. Arthur H. Ruggles, Providence, to John F. Fulton, in September 1958.  Folder includes George Alder Blumer to Harvey Cushing, 1920 April 12; Ruggles to Fulton, 1958 September 20; and Fulton to Ruggles, 1958 September 23. A letter from George Blumer to George Alder Blumer concerning Osler was moved to a folder under George Blumer. George Alder Blumer annotated the context of several of the Osler letters.</p>
            </scopecontent>
         </c>
